          Welcome to the Learning Lab board!


          The GitHub Learning Lab can be found at lab.github.com

          There you can learn new skills by completing fun, realistic projects that are made in real time; in your very own GitHub repository.

          If you have questions about how to use the Learning Lab, or how to create a course depend on the teacher, please open a new topic in this board.

          Before you open a new topic, you may want to check the documentation to see if there is already a guide to help answer your question.

          If you have any questions outside of the Learning Lab, please review the board descriptions here to find what board is best for your topic.
